<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="renderer" content="webkit" />
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Language" content="zh-cn" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content = "IE=edge,chrome=1" />
    <meta name="author" content="vb" />
    <meta name="Copyright" content="visualbusiness" />
    <meta name="Description" content="皓月平台的宗旨。" />
    <meta name="Keywords" content="皓月" />
    <title>皓月平台</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family:'Helvetica Neue','Hiragino Sans GB','Microsoft YaHei','\9ED1\4F53',Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;">
<!--中间区域内容 start-->
<div class="content">
    <div style="width: 1000px;margin: auto;">
        <!--主题内容 start-->
        <div class="main" style="position: relative;">
            <div class="email-main" style="position: relative;width: 510px;height: 636px;background:#4F6499;padding: 18px 12px;-webkit-border-radius: 8px;-moz-border-radius: 8px;border-radius: 8px;margin-top: 5%;left: 25%;">
                <div style="height: 61px;vertical-align: middle;padding: 6px 58px 23px 58px;">
                    <img src="http://view.luna.visualbusiness.cn/uploadfiles/userRegist/Logo.png" style="height: 61px;width: 160px;">
                </div>
                <div style="background: #FFFFFF;-webkit-border-radius: 8px;-moz-border-radius: 8px;border-radius: 8px;padding: 48px 48px 15px 48px;">
                    <p style="font-size: 20px;line-height: 28px;margin:0;padding-bottom: 8px;font-weight: 500;">您好，</p>
                    <p style="line-height: 2em; margin: 0;">
                        您所在商户“为民农家院”申请开通皓月交易直通车的认证资料，经过客服人员核实有误，理由如下：
                    </p>
                    <p style="line-height: 2em; margin: 0;">
                        ${merchantName}
                        <br>
                        ${refuseReason}
                        <br>
                        ${today}
                    </p>
                    <p style="line-height: 2em; margin: 0;">
                        如有疑问，请联系相关工作人员。
                    </p>
                    <p style="line-height: 2em;margin: 12px 0;text-align: right;">
                        <label id="todayText" for="">2016-8-31</label>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--主题内容 end-->
    </div>
</div>
<script>
    var d = new Date();
    var dateText = d.getFullYear()+'.'+(d.getMonth())+'.'+d.getDate();
    document.querySelector('#todayText').innerHTML = dateText;
</script>
<!--中间区域内容 end-->
</body>
</html>